This is a '''list of films produced in the Spanish Revolution'''. In the [[Spanish Revolution of 1936|Spanish Revolution]], the film industry was collectivized by the [[Confederación Nacional del Trabajo|CNT]] and [[Federación Anarquista Ibérica|FAI]]. Between July 1936 and June 1937, 84 films were produced by [[SIE Films]], [[FRIEP]] and [[Spartacus Films]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://archivo.cnt.es/Documentos/cineyanarquismo/anarq_cine_unic.htm |title=El anarquismo en el cine, una experiencia única |last1=Artero |first1=Antonio |publisher=Sindicato de Artes Gráficas, Comunicación y Espectáculos de Madrid - [[Confederación Nacional del Trabajo|CNT/AIT]] |language=Spanish |accessdate=2014-12-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6V5Fo4vTm?url=http://archivo.cnt.es/Documentos/cineyanarquismo/anarq_cine_unic.htm |archivedate=2014-12-25 |deadurl=no |df= }}</ref> Only about 40 films have been preserved and not all them are complete.
